\c 6
\s UJesu uchasisa umlayo wesabatha
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi\x + Mat. 12.1-8. Mark. 2.23-28.\x* ngesabatha lesibili lakuqala edabula emasimini amabele\x + Levi 23.15. 25.2,4.\x*, abafundi bakhe bakha izikhwebu, badla, be\add zi\add*hlikihla ngezandla.
\v 2 Kodwa abathile babaFarisi bathi kubo: Lenzelani okungavunyelwa ukwenziwa ngensuku zesabatha\x + Joha. 5.10.\x*?
\v 3 UJesu wasebaphendula, wathi: Alifundanga lalokho yini, uDavida akwenzayo, mhla elambile yena lababelaye,
\v 4 ukuthi wayangena njani endlini kaNkulunkulu, wathatha izinkwa zokubukiswa, wasesidla, wanika lalabo ababelaye; ezingavunyelwa ukudliwa ngaphandle kwabapristi bodwa?
\v 5 Wasesithi kubo: INdodana yomuntu iyiNkosi leyesabatha\x + Mat. 12.8.\x*.
\s UJesu usilisa ngesabatha
\p
\v 6 Kwasekusithi langelinye isabatha wangena esinagogeni, wafundisa\x + Mat. 12.9-14. Mark. 3.1-6.\x*; njalo kwakukhona umuntu lapho, osandla sakhe sokunene sasitshwabhene\x + 6.8. Joha. 5.3.\x*.
\v 7 Ababhali labaFarisi basebemqaphela\x + 14.1.\x*, ukuthi uzasilisa ngesabatha yini; ukuze bathole \add oko\add*kumbeka icala.
\v 8 Kodwa wayazi imicabango yabo\x + Mat. 9.4.\x*, wathi kumuntu olesandla esitshwabheneyo: Sukuma, ume phakathi. Wasukuma-ke wema.
\v 9 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Ngizalibuza ulutho: Kuvunyelwe yini ngamasabatha ukwenza okulungileyo kumbe ukwenza okubi? Ukusindisa impilo kumbe ukuchitha?
\v 10 Wasebathalaza bonke, wathi kumuntu: Yelula isandla sakho. Wasesenza njalo. Isandla sakhe sasesisiliswa saphila njengesinye\x + Mark. 3.5.\x*.
\v 11 Basebegcwala ubuhlanya\x + 2 Tim.3.9.\x*; bakhulumisana omunye komunye, ukuthi bangamenzani uJesu\x + Mat. 12.14. Mark. 3.6.\x*.
\s Ukukhethwa kwabaphostoli
\p
\v 12 Kwasekusithi ngalezonsuku waphuma waya entabeni ukuyakhuleka\x + Mat. 14.23. Luka 9.18,28; 11.1.\x*; wahlala ubusuku bonke ekukhulekeni kuNkulunkulu\x + Mark. 11.22.\x*.
\v 13 Kwathi sekusile, wabizela kuye abafundi bakhe\x + Mat. 10.1. Mark. 3.13,14.\x*; wakhetha kubo abalitshumi lambili, ababiza futhi ngokuthi ngabaphostoli\x + Mat. 10.2-4. Mark. 3.16-19. Seb. 1.13. Joha. 6.70.\x*;
\v 14 uSimoni laye ambiza ngokuthi nguPetro, loAndreya umfowabo, uJakobe loJohane, uFiliphu loBartolomewu,
\v 15 uMathewu loTomasi, uJakobe okaAlfewu, loSimoni owayethiwa ngumZelothi\x + Mat. 10.4.\x*,
\v 16 uJudasi\x + Joha. 14.22.\x* kaJakobe, loJudasi Iskariyothi, laye owaba ngumnikeli\x + Juda 1. Mat. 10.3. Mark. 3.18.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Wasesehla labo, wema esigcawini, lexuku labafundi bakhe\x + Mat. 5.1.\x*, lexuku elikhulu labantu abavela kuyo yonke iJudiya leJerusalema\x + Mat. 4.25. Mark. 3.7,8.\x*, langaselwandle lweTire leSidoni\x + Mat. 15.21.\x*, ababezile ukumuzwa, lokusiliswa ezifweni zabo;
\v 18 lalabo ababekhathazwa ngomoya abangcolileyo, basebesiliswa.
\v 19 Lexuku lonke ladinga ukumthinta\x + Mat. 14.36.\x*; ngoba kwaphuma amandla kuye, asebasilisa bonke\x + 8.46. Mark. 5.30.\x*.
\s Ababusiswayo labangabusiswayo
\p
\v 20 Yena wasephakamisela amehlo akhe kubafundi bakhe wathi\x + Joha. 6.5. Joha. 11.41; 17.1. Mat. 17.8. Luka 16.23; 18.13. Joha. 4.35.\x*: Libusisiwe, bayanga, ngoba umbuso kaNkulunkulu ungowenu.
\v 21 Libusisiwe, lina elilambileyo khathesi, ngoba lizasuthiswa. Libusisiwe, lina elikhalayo khathesi, ngoba lizahleka\x + Mat. 5.3-12.\x*.
\v 22 Libusisiwe, nxa abantu belizonda, njalo nxa belehlukanisa, belithuka, belahla ibizo lenu ngokungathi libi, ngenxa yeNdodana yomuntu\x + Joha. 16.2.\x*.
\v 23 Thokozani ngalolosuku leqe ngokuthokoza\x + 1.44.\x*; ngoba khangelani, umvuzo wenu mkhulu ezulwini; ngoba oyise benza njalo kubaprofethi.
\v 24 Kodwa maye kini\x + Amos 6.1.\x* lina elinothileyo\x + 12.21. Jak. 5.1.\x*! Ngoba seliyemukele\x + 16.25.Mat. 6.2.\x* induduzo yenu\x + 2.25. Seb. 9.31. Fil. 2.1. 2 Thes. 2.16.\x*.
\v 25 Maye kini, lina elisuthiyo! Ngoba lizalamba\x + Isa. 65.13.\x*. Maye kini, lina elihlekayo khathesi! Ngoba lizalila, likhale\x + Zaga 14.13.\x*.
\v 26 Maye kini, nxa abantu bonke bekhuluma kuhle ngani\x + Joha. 15.19; 17.14. 1 Joha. 4.5.\x*! Ngoba oyise babesenza njalo kubaprofethi bamanga\x + Mat. 7.15.\x*.
\s Ukuthanda izitha
\p
\v 27 Kodwa ngithi kini elizwayo: Thandani izitha zenu, lenze okuhle kwabalizondayo\x + 6.35. Mat. 5.44.\x*,
\v 28 libusise abaliqalekisayo, libakhulekele abaliphatha kubi\x + 6.35. Mat. 5.44.\x*.
\v 29 Okutshaya esihlathini, mnike lesinye\x + 6.29,30. Mat. 5.39-42.\x*; lokwemuka isembatho sakho, ungali lesigqoko sakho.
\v 30 Kodwa mnike wonke ocela kuwe; lokwemuka okwakho, ungabuyi u\add ku\add*bize kuye\x + 1 Kor. 6.7. Mat. 5.39.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Njalo njengalokho lithanda ukuthi abantu benze kini, lani yenzani njalo kubo\x + Mat. 7.12.\x*.
\v 32 Njalo uba lithanda labo abalithandayo\x + Mat. 5.46.\x*, yikubongwa bani elilakho? Ngoba lezoni zithanda labo abazithandayo\x + Mat. 5.46,47.\x*.
\v 33 Njalo uba lisenza okuhle kulabo abenza okuhle kini, yikubongwa bani elilakho? Ngoba lezoni zenza okufananayo\x + Mat. 5.46,47.\x*.
\v 34 Futhi uba liseboleka labo elithemba ukwemukela kubo\x + Mat. 5.42.\x*, yikubongwa bani elilakho? Ngoba lezoni zeboleka izoni, ukuze zemukele izinto ezifananayo.
\v 35 Kodwa thandani izitha zenu\x + 6.27.\x*, lenze okuhle, leboleke, lingalindeli lutho olubuyiselwayo\x + Mat. 5.42.\x*; lomvuzo wenu uzakuba mkhulu, njalo libe ngabantwana\x + Mat. 5.45.\x* boPhezukonke\x + 1.32.\x*; ngoba yena ulobubele kwabangabongiyo lababi\x + 1 Pet. 2.3. Mat. 20.15.\x*.
\v 36 Ngakho banini lesihawu\x + Jak. 5.11.\x*, njengoba laye uYihlo elesihawu\x + Jak. 5.11.\x*.
\s Ukwahlulela abanye
\p
\v 37 Lingahluleli, njalo alisoze lahlulelwe\x + 6.37,38,41,42, Mat. 7.1-5.\x*; lingalahli, njalo alisoze lilahlwe; thethelelani, njalo lizathethelelwa\x + 6.22.68. Seb. 3.13. Mat. 6.14.\x*;
\v 38 phanini, lani lizaphiwa\x + Zaga 19.17.\x*; isilinganiso esihle, sigqitshiwe sahlukuzwa, siphuphuma, bazalipha esifubeni\x + Hlab. 79.12.\x*. Ngoba ngalesosilinganiso elilinganisa ngaso lizalinganiselwa ngaso futhi.
\p
\v 39 Wasebatshela umfanekiso \add wokuthi\add*: Kambe isiphofu singakhokhela isiphofu yini? Kabayikuwela bobabili emgodini yini\x + Mat. 15.14.\x*?
\v 40 Umfundi kamkhulu kulomfundisi wakhe\x + Mat. 10.24.\x*; kodwa wonke opheleleyo uzakuba njengomfundisi wakhe\x + 1 Kor. 1.10. 2 Kor. 13.11. Heb. 13.21. 1 Pet. 5.10.\x*.
\p
\v 41 Njalo ukhangelelani ucezwana oluselihlweni lomfowenu, kodwa ungalunanzeleli ugodo olukwelakho ilihlo?
\v 42 Kumbe ungatsho njani kumfowenu \add ukuthi\add*: Mfowethu, kahle ngikhuphe ucezwana oluselihlweni lakho, wena ungaluboni ugodo oluselihlweni lakho? Mzenzisi, qala ukhuphe ugodo elihlweni lakho, khona-ke uzabona kuhle ukukhupha ucezwana oluselihlweni lomfowenu\x + 6.37,38,41,42, Mat. 7.1-5.\x*.
\p
\v 43 Ngoba kayisiso isihlahla esihle esithela isithelo esibi; futhi kayisiso isihlahla esibi esithela isithelo esihle\x + 6.43,44, Mat. 7.16,18.\x*.
\v 44 Ngoba yileso laleso isihlahla saziwa ngesaso isithelo. Ngoba kabaseli imikhiwa emeveni, futhi kakukhiwa isithelo sevini evikaneni\x + Mat. 12.33.\x*.
\v 45 Umuntu olungileyo uveza okulungileyo kokuligugu elilungileyo lenhliziyo yakhe, lomuntu omubi uveza okubi kokuligugu elibi lenhliziyo yakhe\x + Mat. 12.35.\x*; ngoba umlomo wakhe ukhuluma ngokugcwala kwenhliziyo\x + Mat. 12.34.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso wezindlu ezimbili
\p
\v 46 Kodwa lingibizelani \add ngokuthi\add*: Nkosi, Nkosi, kodwa lingazenzi izinto engizitshoyo\x + Mat. 7.21. Mal. 1.6. Joha. 13.13.\x*?
\v 47 Wonke oza kimi awezwe amazwi ami njalo awenze, ngizalitshengisa ukuthi ufanana lobani;
\v 48 ufanana lomuntu owakha indlu, wagebha watshonisa, wabeka isisekelo phezu kwedwala; kwathi ekufikeni kwempophoma, umfula watshaya kuleyondlu, kodwa wawungelamandla okuyinyikinya; ngoba yayisekelwe phezu kwedwala\x + Mat. 7.24-27.\x*.
\v 49 Kodwa owezwayo njalo angawenzi unjengomuntu owakha indlu emhlabathini ingelasisekelo\x + Mat. 7.26.\x*; umfula wayitshaya, njalo yahle yawa, futhi kwaba kukhulu ukudilika kwaleyondlu\x + Mat. 7.26.\x*.
